WEBVTT

00:00:00.340 --> 00:00:01.700
Well, don't back out.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:12.940
Hey, honey.

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:14.480
Where are you?

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:16.500
I can't wait to

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.440
feel you inside me!

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:20.000
Damn!

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:21.400
What the hell?

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:22.060
Babe?

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:23.200
What's wrong?

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:27.800
He's occupied.

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.100
Sort it out yourself.

00:00:30.140 --> 00:00:30.600
What...

00:00:31.640 --> 00:00:32.200
Why?

00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:33.600
You still wanna go?

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.340
Aren't you afraid 

00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:36.800
he'll record you and

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:38.000
post it online,

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.400
and then you'll

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:40.500
lose all your fans?

00:00:41.700 --> 00:00:42.500
Of course not!

00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:45.100
I... I'm gonna go.

00:01:00.020 --> 00:01:00.500
Damn!

00:01:01.180 --> 00:01:02.480
Someone swooped in?

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:24.600
Should've been faster at Turn 2.

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:27.100
Charles!

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:29.100
Congrats! You won again!

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:31.140
You wanna grab a bite?

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:33.020
I can also get an exclusive!

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.400
Sure.

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:40.800
Is your dad feeling better?

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.700
He's on a new treatment now.

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:46.860
It seems...

00:01:46.860 --> 00:01:49.060
he really wants us to get married.

00:01:52.820 --> 00:01:54.200
I don't really want to

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:55.160
think about

00:01:55.160 --> 00:01:56.220
marriage recently.

00:01:56.220 --> 00:01:57.300
Maybe...

00:01:57.300 --> 00:01:59.240
we can talk about racing instead?

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:00.380
Okay...

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:04.900
Look,

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:06.100
Charles is here, too!

